SELECT DISTINCT
	"P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID 					AS "SURVEY_KEY",
	"ST"."DATE" AS "VISIT_DATE",
	COALESCE("PRD".SURVEY_KEY,'NOT INFORMED') AS "VISIT_PRODUCT",
	SUM("P".RESPONSE_NUMBER) AS "TOTAL_VISITS"
    
 FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_RESPONSES AS "P"
 
 LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT
	"P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID 					AS "SURVEY_KEY",
    "P".RESPONSE
 FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_RESPONSES AS "P"
 WHERE "P".QUESTION_ORDER = 0  AND "P".RESPONSE IS NOT NULL) AS "PRD" ON "P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID = "PRD".SURVEY_KEY
 
 INNER JOIN (SELECT 
	  "ST".SURVEY_TARGET_ID as "SURVEY_KEY",
	  CAST(TRIM(CAST(LEFT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),4)||'-'||
	  SUBSTRING(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)) FROM 5 FOR 2) ||'-'||
	  RIGHT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),2) AS VARCHAR(10))) AS DATE FORMAT 'yyyy-mm-dd') AS "DATE",
	  "ST".SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS as "TARGET_LAST_MODIFIED_TS",
	  CAST("ST".SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYYMMDD') AS "MODIFIED_DATE",
	  "ST".START_DATE_ID,
	  "ST".END_DATE_ID,
	  "ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID,
	  "ST".REVIEW_STATUS,
	  "ST".MANAGER_TERRITORY_ID,
	  "ST".EMPLOYEE_TERRITORY_ID,
	  "ST".TERRITORY_ID
FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_TARGETS AS "ST"
WHERE "ST".COUNTRY_CODE = 'BR'  AND 
	"ST".SURVEY_TARGET_NAME LIKE '%GSO U%' AND
	LEFT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),6) > '201901') AS "ST" ON "P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID = "ST".SURVEY_KEY

WHERE "P".QUESTION_ID = '12215'
GROUP BY "P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID,
			"ST"."DATE",
		COALESCE("PRD".SURVEY_KEY,'NOT INFORMED');

SELECT 
	  QUESTION_ID,
      CREATED_DATE AS "QUESTION_CREATED_DATE",
      QUESTION_NAME,     
      SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS	AS "QUESTION_LAST_MODIFIED_TS",
      QUESTION_TEXT,
      QUESTION_ORDER 		AS "QUESTION_ORDER",
      CASE
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 0 THEN 'PRODUCT'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 1 THEN 'COCO'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 2 THEN 'SOB'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 3 THEN 'QTC'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 4 THEN 'GSO'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 5 THEN 'VISITS'
      ELSE	'' END 	AS "QUESTION_TYPE",
      CASE
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 0 THEN 'PRODUCT' 
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 1 THEN 'OCV'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 2 THEN 'Foco da Discussão'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 3 THEN 'Fechamento'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 4 THEN 'GSO'
      WHEN QUESTION_ORDER = 5 THEN 'Visitas'
      ELSE '' END	AS "TIPO_QUESTAO"
FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_SURVEY_QUESTION
WHERE COUNTRY_CODE = 'BR' AND
QUESTION_ORDER < 6 AND 
DELETED_IND = 0

SELECT RX_EXTERNAL_ID,
      USER_ID,
 	  SOURCE_USER_AID										AS "SF_SOURCE_USER_AID",
      USER_NAME,
      FIRST_NAME,
      NAME,
      LAST_NAME,      
      COUNTRY,
      STATE_PROVINCE,
      UPPER(CITY) 											AS "CITY",
      POSTAL_CODE,
      ACTIVE_IND,
      EMAIL,
      EMPLOYEE_NUMBER_AID,
      USER_IDENTIFIER_AID,
      CORE_GSK_FUNCTIONAL_PROFILE,
      PROFILE_NAME
 FROM  LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_USER
WHERE ACTIVE_IND = 1;
 ;

select DISTINCT MUDID	AS 'RX_EXTERNAL_ID',
 	  UF
from Dim_Cad_Funcionarios

SELECT 
     ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO										AS RX_EXTERNAL_ID,
	 CICLO,
     CICLO + '-' + ROW_ID_TERRITORIO						AS SALES_FORCE_KEY,
     CICLO + '-' + ROW_ID_TERRITORIO						AS SF_KEY,
	 ROW_ID_TERRITORIO,
     ROW_ID_GD,
     NOME_GD,
     NOME_GR,
	 CASE
     WHEN Len(COALESCE(TERRITORIO_GD,'0123456789')) = 0 THEN TERRITORIO_GD
     ELSE Right(TERRITORIO_GD, 6) END AS TERRITORIO_GD,
	 CASE
	 WHEN Len(COALESCE(TERRITORIO_GR,'0123456789')) = 0 THEN TERRITORIO_GR
     ELSE Right(TERRITORIO_GR, 6)END AS TERRITORIO_GR,
     BU,
     CASE
	 WHEN DIVISÃO = 'REDES' THEN 'REDES DIRETAS'
     ELSE DIVISÃO END  AS DIVISÃO,
     CASE
	 WHEN Len(COALESCE(TERRITORIO,'0123456789')) = 0 THEN TERRITORIO
     ELSE Right(TERRITORIO, 6) END AS TERRITORIO,
	 NOME_REPRESENTANTE										AS NOME_REP        
FROM Dim_Cad_Forca_Vendas
WHERE STATUS = 'A'
  AND CICLO >= '201901'
  AND (BU = 'FARMA' OR BU = 'BIOTECH');

SELECT 
	"CM".CALL_SUMMARY_ID,
	 "CM".PARENT_CALL_AID,
	 "CM".LOCAL_CALL_DATE_ID,
	 "CM".CALL_DATE_ID,
	 "CM".TERRITORY_ID,
	 LEFT(CAST("CM".CALL_DATE_ID as CHAR(8)),6) 		AS "CYCLE",
	 ((LEFT(CAST("CM".CALL_DATE_ID as CHAR(8)),6)||'-')||"CM".TERRITORY_ID)	AS "SALES_FORCE_KEY",
	 LEFT(CAST("CM".CALL_DATE_ID as CHAR(8)),6)	AS "DATE",
	 "CM".LOCAL_CALL_TIME_ID,
	 "CM".ACCOUNT_ID,
	 "CM".CALL_NAME,
	 "CM".RX_CALL_TYPE,
	 "CM".CALL_STATUS,
	 "CM".ATTENDEE_TYPE,
	 "CM".CLM_IND,
	 "CM".SAMPLE_CALL_IND,
	 "CM".CALL_TYPE,
	 "CM".DETAILED_PRODUCTS,
	 "CM".DURATION,
	 "CM".CREATED_DATE_ID,
	 "CM".CREATED_DATE_TIME_ID,
	 "CM".LAST_MODIFIED_DATE_ID,
	 "CM".LAST_MODIFIED_DATE_TIME_ID,
	 "CM".PRE_CALL_NOTES,
	 "CM".NEXT_CALL_NOTES,
	 'Completed_vod'										AS "REVIEW_STATUS",
	 "AC".ACCOUNT_NAME,
	 "AC".RX_LEGAL_ID,
	 "KEY".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME,
	 "KEY".QUESTION_ID,
	 COALESCE("KEY".PRODUCT_NAME,'NOT INFORMED') AS "PRODUCT",
	 "KEY".CALL_DATE,
	 'CALLS'				AS "ORIGEM"

FROM  
	LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_SUMMARY "CM"

LEFT JOIN (
			SELECT 
				ACCOUNT_ID,
	 			NAME AS "ACCOUNT_NAME",
     			RX_LEGAL_ID
			FROM 
				LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_ACCOUNT
			WHERE
				COUNTRY_CODE = 'BR'
  				AND DELETED_IND = 0
  			) as "AC" ON "CM".ACCOUNT_ID = "AC".ACCOUNT_ID

LEFT JOIN (
			SELECT
				"CM".CALL_SUMMARY_ID,
				"KM".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME,
				CASE
				WHEN "KM".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Tentativa de GSO - Expositiva' THEN '12209'
			    WHEN "KM".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Tentativa de GSO - Interativa' THEN '12213'
			    WHEN "KM".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Lembrança da marca' THEN '12210'
			    WHEN "KM".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Good Sell Outcome (GSO)' THEN '12212'
			    ELSE "KM".KEY_MESSAGE_NAME END AS "QUESTION_ID",
			    "PC".PRODUCT_NAME,
			    "CM".CALL_DATE_ID as "CALL_DATE",
			    "CM".TERRITORY_ID  
			
			FROM 
				LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_CALL_MESSAGE as "CM"

			LEFT JOIN (
						SELECT DISTINCT
						    KEY_MESSAGE_ID 	as "MESSAGE_ID",
						    KEY_MESSAGE_ID,
						    KEY_MESSAGE_NAME
						
						FROM 
							LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_KEY_MESSAGE
						WHERE 	
							(KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Visita não promocional' OR
							 KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Lembrança da marca' OR
						     KEY_MESSAGE_NAME LIKE '*GSO*')
					 	) AS "KM" ON "CM".KEY_MESSAGE_ID = "KM".KEY_MESSAGE_ID
        
			LEFT JOIN (
						SELECT 
							PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID,
				 			PRODUCT_NAME
						FROM 
						LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG
					  ) AS "PC" ON "CM".PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID = "PC".PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID
						
			
						WHERE 
						(EXISTS (
									SELECT DISTINCT
									    KEY_MESSAGE_ID 	as "MESSAGE_ID",
									    KEY_MESSAGE_ID,
									    KEY_MESSAGE_NAME
									FROM 
										LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_KEY_MESSAGE
									WHERE 	
										(KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Visita não promocional' OR
										 KEY_MESSAGE_NAME = 'Lembrança da marca' OR
									     KEY_MESSAGE_NAME LIKE '*GSO*')
									     AND KEY_MESSAGE_ID = "CM".KEY_MESSAGE_ID)
								) 
						AND
						(EXISTS (
									SELECT 
										PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID,
							 			PRODUCT_NAME
									FROM 
										LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.D_PRODUCT_CATALOG
						      		WHERE PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID =	"CM".PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID)
						 		)
						 AND
						 LEFT(CAST(CALL_DATE_ID as CHAR(8)),6) > '201901'
		) AS "KEY" ON "CM".CALL_SUMMARY_ID = "KEY".CALL_SUMMARY_ID
  
WHERE 
	LEFT(CAST("CM".CALL_DATE_ID as CHAR(8)),6)>= '201901' AND
	"CM".COUNTRY_CODE = 'BR' AND 
  	"CM".CALL_STATUS = 'Submitted_vod' AND 
  	"CM".DELETED_IND = 0;

SELECT 
	"P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID 					AS "SURVEY_KEY",
    "P".QUESTION_ID,					
    "P".SOURCE_CREATED_TS,
    "P".SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS			AS "RESPONSE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS",
    "P".SOURCE_CREATED_BY_AID AS "SOURCE_USER_AID",
    "P".QUESTION_RESPONSE_ID,          
    "P".RESPONSE_NAME,
    "P".RESPONSE_NUMBER,
    "P".RESPONSE,
    COALESCE("PRD".SURVEY_KEY,'NOT INFORMED') AS "PRODUCT",
    "P".QUESTION_ORDER				AS "RESPONSE_QUESTION_ORDER",
	"ST"."DATE",
	"ST".TARGET_LAST_MODIFIED_TS,
	"ST".MODIFIED_DATE,
	"ST".START_DATE_ID,
	"ST".END_DATE_ID,
	"ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID,
	"ST".REVIEW_STATUS,
	"ST".MANAGER_TERRITORY_ID,
	"ST".EMPLOYEE_TERRITORY_ID,
	"ST".TERRITORY_ID,
 	("ST".MODIFIED_DATE - "ST"."DATE" ) AS "DATE_DIFF",
 	CASE
 	WHEN ("ST".MODIFIED_DATE - ADD_MONTHS("ST"."DATE" - EXTRACT(DAY FROM "ST"."DATE")+1,6)) > 7 THEN 'N'
 	ELSE 'S' END AS "FLAG_PREMIO",
 	LEFT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),6)||'-'||TRIM("ST".EMPLOYEE_TERRITORY_ID) AS "SALES_FORCE_KEY",
 	LEFT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),6)||'-'||TRIM("ST".EMPLOYEE_TERRITORY_ID) AS "RESPONSES_KEY",
	'SURVEYS'				AS "ORIGEM"
    
 FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_RESPONSES AS "P"
 
 LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT
	"P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID 					AS "SURVEY_KEY",
    "P".RESPONSE
 FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_RESPONSES AS "P"
 WHERE "P".QUESTION_ORDER = 0  AND "P".RESPONSE IS NOT NULL) AS "PRD" ON "P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID = "PRD".SURVEY_KEY
 
 INNER JOIN (SELECT 
	  "ST".SURVEY_TARGET_ID as "SURVEY_KEY",
	  CAST(TRIM(CAST(LEFT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),4)||'-'||
	  SUBSTRING(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)) FROM 5 FOR 2) ||'-'||
	  RIGHT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),2) AS VARCHAR(10))) AS DATE FORMAT 'yyyy-mm-dd') AS "DATE",
	  "ST".SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS as "TARGET_LAST_MODIFIED_TS",
	  CAST("ST".SOURCE_LAST_MODIFIED_TS AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYYMMDD') AS "MODIFIED_DATE",
	  "ST".START_DATE_ID,
	  "ST".END_DATE_ID,
	  "ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID,
	  "ST".REVIEW_STATUS,
	  "ST".MANAGER_TERRITORY_ID,
	  "ST".EMPLOYEE_TERRITORY_ID,
	  "ST".TERRITORY_ID
FROM LATAMCRMFBICNTRYBRVW.F_SURVEY_TARGETS AS "ST"
WHERE "ST".COUNTRY_CODE = 'BR'  AND 
	"ST".SURVEY_TARGET_NAME LIKE '%GSO U%' AND
	LEFT(CAST("ST".REVIEW_DATE_ID AS CHAR(8)),6) > '201901') AS "ST" ON "P".SURVEY_TARGET_ID = "ST".SURVEY_KEY;

SELECT
    TOP 100  
    chave.[PRIMARY KEY],
    valor.*
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gsksynapsestorage/synapse/workspaces/gsk-synapse/warehouse/dash.email1to1/dim_audit_end.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) AS valor
left join (
  SELECT
	   ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY(temp.[CRM_UNIV])) AS 'PRIMARY KEY'	
      ,temp.[CRM_UNIV]
  FROM 
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gsksynapsestorage/synapse/workspaces/gsk-synapse/warehouse/dash.email1to1/dim_audit_end.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
   ) as temp
   GROUP BY temp.[CRM_UNIV]) AS [chave] ON valor.[CRM_UNIV] = chave.[CRM_UNIV];
